citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 4:00 PM on 18 April
2023. Upon speaking to the current residents at the official address, the registrant has not lived there for months.
Repeated phone calls to the registrant for the past week have not been answered, and currently the phone appears to be
disconnected or out of service.
End Section
